name: Mansuki
description: $mansuki is a memecoin on the Solana blockchain. It is centered around the personal brand of Mansuki, a singer-songwriter, artist, entertainer, and creator who operates under the handle @rayligaya on X. Mansuki taps into the early wave of Solana's Internet Capital Markets (ICM). The token binds to content creation activities, such as music production, networking, and live-streaming on Pump.fun, positioning itself as a community-driven meme token tied to the creator's identity. As of late November 2025, it has achieved over 600 holders and a Telegram community exceeding 500 members, with a notable presence in the Philippines. Liquidity is locked, along with 24 million tokens locked until Mansuki's birthday on March 23, 2026. Community efforts and activities include token giveaways, buybacks, and locks/burns to support the supply. The associated website is mansuki.com, and the official Telegram channel is t.me/mansukiofficial. Mansuki's collective following across active social media platforms totals approximately 620,000 followers, encompassing X (11K+ followers), Facebook (390K+ likes) and Instagram (85K+ followers).
